RACE.FOOTNOTES: NORDIC LIGHT never far back with a rail run, angled out around the far turn, rallied in the stretch run and drove clear. MIGHTY RIOT tried to keep up for a half but gave way willingly and faded from far turn. B G LEE could not keep up to far turn, gave way past quarter pole to wire.
